dct_title_s: Pilot chart of the North Pacific Ocean
dct_description_sm: prepared from data furnished by the Hydrographic Office of the Navy Department and the Weather Bureau of the Department of Agriculture.
Includes text and inset maps showing "Isobars and isotherms for the month" and "Gales."
